{
  "uid": "meridian-errors",
  "title": "Errors",
  "tags": ["meridian", "ops-05", "v1"],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": false,
  "time": { "from": "now-6h", "to": "now" },
  "refresh": "30s",
  "timezone": "browser",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "realm",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "meridian-prometheus" },
        "query": "label_values(meridian_ccu, realm)",
        "includeAll": true,
        "refresh": 2
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Server log error rate (Loki)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "meridian-loki" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (process) (rate({realm=~\"$realm\"} | json | level=~\"ERROR|CRITICAL\" [5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{process}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Opcode error / drop rate",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "meridian-prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (opcode) (rate(meridian_opcode_errors_total{realm=~\"$realm\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "err {{opcode}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "sum by (opcode, reason) (rate(meridian_opcode_dropped_total{realm=~\"$realm\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "drop {{opcode}}/{{reason}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Client ERROR/CRITICAL ingest (count only, no payload)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "meridian-prometheus" },
      "description": "Server-side count of client-reported ERROR/CRITICAL events. No PII, no chat, no payload (telemetry-privacy.md §2a/§3).",
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (severity, build, platform) (rate(meridian_client_log_ingest_total{realm=~\"$realm\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{severity}} {{build}}/{{platform}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Crash rate by build — future (blocked on client crashpad #109)",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Client crash rate — not charted at M0 (#297)\n\nThe client crash-count metric is a **name reservation** in the metrics catalog but has **no emit path** yet: it is blocked on the client crash handler (**crashpad, #109**). Until the client captures and ships crash reports there is nothing to count.\n\nPer `telemetry-privacy.md §4` the crash **sink** is a Sentry-compatible endpoint, **not** this Prometheus stack — this counter is only the server-side *received-count* once #109 lands. This panel becomes a real crash-rate timeseries then."
      }
    }
  ]
}
